    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street,</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden, N.J.,</name>
                    <date when="1885-10-13" rend="right">October 13, 1885.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Thank the Columbus Buggy Co., and their workmen, for the beautiful looking and
                practically perfect buggy furnished me. I get out in it every day&#8212;my only
                exercise&#8212;and I find it the easiest riding vehicle I ever sat in. Thank them
                for a most opportune kindness and generosity to me. </p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman.</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
